Each user has a socket ID
When a new user connects have a contructor create a new object


Server Side
On socket connection 
//send to everyone
io.emit('create_user', {id:socket.id, name: name });

Client Side
io.sockets.on('create_user', function(user) {
	//create a new Object
	var user.id = new User(user.name, user.id, ___ some other stuff);

})




